{"id":232661503,"title":"社工系v.s.社會學系","content":"大家好\n本人今年大二\n想在大四最閒的時候去補公職的「社會行政」\n而本科系的課業又不重\n所以想先修相關的輔系\n以免到補習時對考科太陌生\n但問題來了\n我不知道我應該輔\n社工系？\n還是\n社會學系？\n哪個才對我以後考公職比較有幫助？\n我有對比過公職的考科\n和兩系輔系的科目\n兩系都有和公職考科重疊\n如下\nhttps://i.imgur.com/USy1Ed6.jpg\n上圖是社工系的\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/Wqu0Qhq.jpg\n上圖是社會學系的\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/KSTHGWJ.jpg\n而上圖是公職考科\n\n這樣重疊到\n我實在不知道應該要選哪一個？\n而這兩系的差別又在哪裡？\n\n拜託社會學系或社工系的同學們給個建議\n真的感激不盡🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏","excerpt":"大家好，本人今年大二，想在大四最閒的時候去補公職的「社會行政」而本科系的課業又不重，所以想先修相關的輔系，以免到補習時對考科太陌生，但問題來了，我不知道我應該輔，社工系？還是，社會學系？哪個才對我以後","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"a62a724b-4fdd-4044-b6d3-19483aa7f0df","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-10T13:55:56.572Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-10T13:55:56.572Z","commentCount":15,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["社工","社會學","輔大","發問","課程"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"輔仁大學","forumAlias":"fju","school":"輔仁大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":true,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/USy1Ed6.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/Wqu0Qhq.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/KSTHGWJ.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"66fd9132-ad9b-46fb-820f-fd6aa0df67fd","url":"https://i.imgur.com/USy1Ed6l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/USy1Ed6l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/USy1Ed6l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-10T13:55:56.572Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-10T13:55:56.572Z"},{"id":"66fd9132-ad9b-46fb-820f-fd6aa0df67fd","url":"https://i.imgur.com/USy1Ed6.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/USy1Ed6","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/USy1Ed6l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-10T13:55:56.572Z","updatedAt":"2019-1